sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 User
    actor WsC as 🤖 Workspace Claude
    participant WS as 🐍 ws.py (client)
    participant D as 🛰️ ws-daemon
    participant FS as 📂 Filesystem
    participant Bend as 🏗️ bend serve

    User->>WsC: also add hs-entities:brbrown/my-feature
    WsC->>WS: add <name> hs-entities:branch
    WS->>FS: git clone + bend yarn (parallel)
    WS->>FS: discover, merge into cache
    WS->>WS: compute combined pkg paths (old + new)
    WS->>D: restart_serve RPC (combined pkg list)
    D->>Bend: killpg SIGTERM → SIGKILL
    D->>Bend: spawn fresh bend reactor serve --enable-tools ...
    Bend->>FS: new <pid>-introspection in route-configs/
    D-->>WS: {ok, servePid}
    WS-->>WsC: add JSON (per-repo results)
    WsC->>User: updated report
